// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5207 — Mass File Rename (alphv)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4c8ba294-5848-5519-9ba8-9109363803aa

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
